No. 68,

Misc.

Orozco v. Texas. Charles W. Tessmer for petitioner. Crawford C. Martin, Attorney General of Texas, Nola White, First Assistant Attorney General, A. J. Carubbi, Jr., Executive Assistant Attorney General, and Robert C. Flowers and Lonny F. Zwiener, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.

Ct. Crim App. Tex. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted and case transferred to appellate docket.
